  m_text: "Make me a potion and I'll help you get out!\n\nYou'll need a dark blue
    liquid, something that grows on a tree, and a powder the color of snow. You might
    have to climb to find one of the ingredients. \n\nPut them all in the cauldron
    and then give me the completed potion."
